From 74640aada0d18f6b1bc5e76131520f513cef1160 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nikolay Amiantov <ab@fmap.me>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 15:58:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add Sony ARW6 (LLVC v3) lossy decoder

Reverse-engineered 'Compressed HQ' (Sony LLVC v3, raw SubIFD compression
32766) decoder, ported from a prototype verified bit-exact against the
Adobe DNG Converter. Line-based inverse 5/3 wavelet pipeline with an
adaptive entropy coder, flipped vertical polyphase and a luma/chroma
combine; the per-band 16-byte header gives the entropy offset and
per-orientation quantizers. Wires compression 32766 into ArwDecoder.

Black/white levels for the linearized output come from the camera
definition's arw6 mode, not the SR2 tags.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 rawler/src/decoders/arw.rs                  |  14 +-
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/curve_bd12.rs | 266 +++++++++++++++
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/entropy.rs    | 198 ++++++++++++
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/header.rs     | 215 +++++++++++++
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/idwt.rs       | 178 ++++++++++
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/mod.rs        | 339 +++++++++++++++++++-
 rawler/src/decompressors/arw6/reader.rs     |  72 +++++
 7 files changed, 1274 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)
