+//! inverse-transformed ([`idwt`]); luma = fused combine of A and B
+//! ([`idwt::stream_luma`]); chroma R/B = `avg(two greens) + 2 * chroma`. The
+//! decoded 12-bit companded values are linearized through a codec curve
